06:09.000 --> 06:12.000
because academic education is really fundamental,

06:13.000 --> 06:19.000
and it, in fact, prepares a person to be able to engage in different areas of activity,

06:20.000 --> 06:23.000
which are defined by his specialty.

06:23.000 --> 06:27.000
When we talk about business education and the teaching of business education,

06:28.000 --> 06:29.000
the situation is fundamentally different.

06:30.000 --> 06:40.000
Business education does not imply that I will invest in a person the knowledge that he should have received.

06:41.000 --> 06:46.000
The problem arises with the fact that there is a specialist here,

06:46.000 --> 06:53.000
and, accordingly, I need to improve the skills that he has,

06:54.000 --> 06:58.000
to specify, to specialize the knowledge that he has,

06:59.000 --> 07:02.000
because, naturally, if a specialist comes to work in a company,

07:03.000 --> 07:11.000
he already has his own traditions, his own methods of approach to solving the tasks that will be faced by him,

07:11.000 --> 07:17.000
and it is necessary to pass on these already developed skills, knowledge, methods.

07:18.000 --> 07:21.000
Then they can be changed, then they can be modified,

07:22.000 --> 07:25.000
but only then, in order not to invent a bicycle from scratch.

07:26.000 --> 07:29.000
In this regard, business education is always practical.

07:30.000 --> 07:33.000
I do not take a person who knows absolutely nothing,

07:34.000 --> 07:37.000
and I do not prepare a person who I need from him.

07:38.000 --> 07:43.000
If we work in a company, then, naturally, in the event of a vacancy,

07:44.000 --> 07:50.000
