07:51.000 --> 07:54.000
But, then the specifics begin.

07:55.000 --> 07:58.000
The specifics of the company, the specifics of the market, the specifics of the product, the specifics of the services.

07:59.000 --> 08:05.000
And in order for a person to get involved as quickly as possible in the most effective functioning,

08:05.000 --> 08:08.000
he needs to pass on these specifics as quickly as possible.

08:09.000 --> 08:14.000
These are the tasks that are solved by learning in business processes.

08:15.000 --> 08:19.000
Therefore, in addition to this important distinction between academic education and business education,

08:20.000 --> 08:29.000
the main criterion that testifies to the effectiveness of learning is the modification of the behavior of the employee.

08:30.000 --> 08:34.000
Moreover, in this case, we are talking about the modification of professional behavior.

08:35.000 --> 08:44.000
A person quickly acquires, refines those skills, those actions, those ways of seeing,

08:45.000 --> 08:50.000
which he needs for the successful performance of the function that is assigned to him.

08:51.000 --> 08:57.000
The faster this modification of behavior is carried out, the more successful the education.

08:58.000 --> 09:02.000
Success here depends on two factors, the main two factors.

09:02.000 --> 09:04.000
Naturally, there can be many factors.

09:05.000 --> 09:13.000
The first is, of course, related to the speed of the formation of the necessary skills, the necessary ways of reacting.

09:14.000 --> 09:17.000
And the second factor is related to the stability of these skills.

09:18.000 --> 09:24.000
If I was prepared today and, accordingly, passed on those skills, but did not work well enough,

09:24.000 --> 09:37.000
then these skills will fail, there will be a backlash, and I will still have to get the results that I need on my own mistakes, on my own experience.

09:38.000 --> 09:47.000
If, for example, we made a mistake in the contract, which is entitled to a large amount, then the price of this mistake can be great.

09:48.000 --> 09:57.000
