is closely related to Skinner.

29:26.000 --> 29:30.000
If we talk about the originator of behaviorism,

29:31.000 --> 29:36.000
it is John Watson, who introduced the concept of behaviorism

29:37.000 --> 29:42.000
and gave the requirements that were then developed,

